===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}

# The third [[planet]] in order from the [[Sun]], upon which [[human]]s live.

====Quotations====
*'''1914''' — [[w:Edgar Rice Burroughs|Edgar Rice Burroughs]], ''[[s:At the Earth's Core|At the Earth's Core]]''
*: "How thick is the '''Earth's''' crust, Perry?" I asked.
*'''1934''' — [[w:H. P. Lovecraft|H. P. Lovecraft]], ''[[s:Through the Gates of the Silver Key|Through the Gates of the Silver Key]]'', Ch 6
*: He thought that his calculations would let him perform a voyage with a light-wave envelope such as no being of Yaddidi had ever performed - a bodily voyage through nameless eons and across incredible galactic reaches to the solar system and the '''Earth''' itself.
*'''1985''' — [[w:Ronald Reagan|Ronald Reagan]], ''[[s:Ronald Reagan's Fourth State of the Union Speech|Fourth State of the Union Speech]]''
*: Our second American Revolution will push on to new possibilities not only on '''Earth''' but in the next frontier of space.

